00:01:33.306 --> 00:01:35.416 A:middle
screen, so at times, it was

00:01:35.416 --> 00:01:36.236 A:middle
pretty cumbersome when you'd

00:01:36.236 --> 00:01:37.186 A:middle
unlock the phone, right?

00:01:37.636 --> 00:01:38.706 A:middle
