00:01:43.656 --> 00:01:45.806 A:middle
them, one at a time, or if you

00:01:45.806 --> 00:01:47.146 A:middle
wanted to reply, you launched

00:01:47.146 --> 00:01:48.306 A:middle
into the app to take action.

00:01:49.716 --> 00:01:52.036 A:middle
