it makes a ton of sense.

00:14:19.516 --> 00:14:20.306 A:middle
So, what do they all have in

00:14:20.306 --> 00:14:20.726 A:middle
common?

00:14:21.066 --> 00:14:22.296 A:middle
Well, all those notifications,

