app.

00:14:31.026 --> 00:14:34.806 A:middle
So, now that you're sending out

00:14:34.946 --> 00:14:35.986 A:middle
really great content.

00:14:36.126 --> 00:14:37.616 A:middle
It's important to consider when

00:14:37.736 --> 00:14:38.846 A:middle
you're sending that content.

00:14:39.256 --> 00:14:40.516 A:middle
So, be considerate when you

00:14:40.516 --> 00:14:41.826 A:middle
deliver notifications.

00:14:42.676 --> 00:14:43.626 A:middle
And reminders is great.

