I missed a few sessions.

00:15:41.446 --> 00:15:42.766 A:middle
And rather than continuing to

00:15:42.766 --> 00:15:44.186 A:middle
send me notifications that I'm

00:15:44.186 --> 00:15:45.826 A:middle
not interacting with, they

00:15:45.826 --> 00:15:46.716 A:middle
decided to pause them.

00:15:47.736 --> 00:15:49.216 A:middle
And I just think that's really

00:15:49.216 --> 00:15:49.816 A:middle
considerate.

00:15:50.236 --> 00:15:51.326 A:middle
Because I could totally

00:15:51.326 --> 00:15:52.546 A:middle
understand the argument right,

00:15:52.786 --> 00:15:53.776 A:middle
why they might want to send me

00:15:53.776 --> 00:15:55.586 A:middle
more notifications at a time

00:15:55.586 --> 00:15:56.936 A:middle
like this and really encourage

00:15:56.936 --> 00:15:58.416 A:middle
me to get back and re-engage

00:15:58.416 --> 00:15:58.976 A:middle
with the app.

00:15:59.556 --> 00:16:00.806 A:middle
But with the new tuning features

00:15:59.556 --> 00:16:00.806 A:middle
But with the new tuning features

00:16:00.806 --> 00:16:02.366 A:middle
we announced, if I get annoyed

00:16:02.366 --> 00:16:03.826 A:middle
by those notifications, I can

00:16:03.826 --> 00:16:05.666 A:middle
easily turn them all off.

00:16:06.346 --> 00:16:07.936 A:middle
So, for them, doing the right

00:16:07.976 --> 00:16:09.846 A:middle
thing in the short term, while

00:16:09.846 --> 00:16:11.046 A:middle
it might seem like the harder

00:16:11.046 --> 00:16:12.686 A:middle
decision to make, I think it's

00:16:12.686 --> 00:16:13.676 A:middle
going to pay off in the long

00:16:13.676 --> 00:16:13.896 A:middle
run.

00:16:14.526 --> 00:16:16.586 A:middle
So, in all cases, it's really

00:16:16.586 --> 00:16:18.416 A:middle
important to consider how and

00:16:18.536 --> 00:16:19.656 A:middle
when you're delivering

00:16:19.786 --> 00:16:20.506 A:middle
notifications.

00:16:20.806 --> 00:16:23.746 A:middle
And finally, we want to make

00:16:23.746 --> 00:16:25.116 A:middle
sure your people are in control

00:16:25.116 --> 00:16:26.186 A:middle
of the content that they're

00:16:26.186 --> 00:16:26.726 A:middle
receiving.

00:16:26.946 --> 00:16:28.136 A:middle
I mean there's a real trust

00:16:28.136 --> 00:16:29.376 A:middle
relationship that's created when

00:16:29.376 --> 00:16:30.546 A:middle
someone allows notifications

00:16:30.546 --> 00:16:31.106 A:middle
from your app.

00:16:31.596 --> 00:16:33.186 A:middle
They're making space for you to

00:16:33.186 --> 00:16:33.986 A:middle
interrupt them with your

00:16:33.986 --> 00:16:34.856 A:middle
content, right?

00:16:35.296 --> 00:16:36.356 A:middle
And as we've discussed, it

00:16:36.356 --> 00:16:37.856 A:middle
should be really valuable.

00:16:38.736 --> 00:16:40.446 A:middle
But not all things have that

00:16:40.446 --> 00:16:41.716 A:middle
same level of value or

00:16:41.716 --> 00:16:43.606 A:middle
importance to all people.

00:16:44.236 --> 00:16:45.396 A:middle
So, let's talk about giving

00:16:45.396 --> 00:16:46.706 A:middle
everyone control on how their

00:16:46.706 --> 00:16:48.086 A:middle
content is delivered, right?

00:16:48.446 --> 00:16:49.486 A:middle
So, we've redesigned settings

00:16:49.486 --> 00:16:50.786 A:middle
this year to more clearly

00:16:50.786 --> 00:16:52.676 A:middle
visualize the different delivery

00:16:52.676 --> 00:16:53.856 A:middle
methods of notifications.

00:16:54.296 --> 00:16:55.736 A:middle
We hope that with more clear and

00:16:55.736 --> 00:16:57.876 A:middle
graphic UI, it will make it

00:16:57.876 --> 00:16:59.306 A:middle
easier for people to adjust how

00:16:59.306 --> 00:17:00.246 A:middle
they're receiving your different

00:16:59.306 --> 00:17:00.246 A:middle
they're receiving your different

00:17:00.246 --> 00:17:00.886 A:middle
notifications.

00:17:01.806 --> 00:17:02.966 A:middle
And if you notice at the bottom

00:17:02.966 --> 00:17:04.826 A:middle
here, we've also added a link to

00:17:04.826 --> 00:17:06.425 A:middle
your third-party custom

00:17:06.425 --> 00:17:07.366 A:middle
notification settings.

00:17:07.826 --> 00:17:10.366 A:middle
And providing that link is even

00:17:10.366 --> 00:17:12.086 A:middle
more important now because of

00:17:12.086 --> 00:17:13.205 A:middle
our new tuning UI.

00:17:13.205 --> 00:17:14.846 A:middle
Because if someone decides to

00:17:14.846 --> 00:17:17.146 A:middle
tap turn off, we don't just

00:17:17.146 --> 00:17:18.496 A:middle
immediately stop all the

00:17:18.496 --> 00:17:19.886 A:middle
notifications from that app, but

00:17:19.886 --> 00:17:21.356 A:middle
we present a confirmation step.

00:17:22.076 --> 00:17:23.356 A:middle
So, in this action sheet, you

00:17:23.356 --> 00:17:24.736 A:middle
could choose to turn off all

00:17:24.736 --> 00:17:25.596 A:middle
notifications from the

00:17:25.596 --> 00:17:28.106 A:middle
particular app, or tap a button,

00:17:28.256 --> 00:17:30.316 A:middle
to go into that app's particular

00:17:30.386 --> 00:17:31.726 A:middle
custom notification settings.

00:17:32.086 --> 00:17:33.376 A:middle
And again, we want people to be

00:17:33.376 --> 00:17:34.856 A:middle
in control of the types of

00:17:34.906 --> 00:17:36.116 A:middle
content that they receive.

00:17:36.706 --> 00:17:37.816 A:middle
So, while we hope that turn off

00:17:37.816 --> 00:17:39.196 A:middle
everything button is a last

00:17:39.196 --> 00:17:40.926 A:middle
resort, we want to encourage

00:17:40.926 --> 00:17:42.376 A:middle
people to get into your app

00:17:42.376 --> 00:17:44.276 A:middle
settings and customize the

00:17:44.276 --> 00:17:45.936 A:middle
notification categories you have

00:17:45.936 --> 00:17:47.016 A:middle
in a more granular way.

00:17:47.746 --> 00:17:49.176 A:middle
So, with this extra visibility

00:17:49.306 --> 00:17:51.076 A:middle
you know it's really important

00:17:51.076 --> 00:17:51.976 A:middle
to make sure these settings

00:17:51.976 --> 00:17:52.966 A:middle
pages are well-designed.

00:17:53.626 --> 00:17:54.296 A:middle
So, let's look at a few

00:17:54.296 --> 00:17:54.686 A:middle
examples.

00:17:55.966 --> 00:17:58.066 A:middle
ESPN is an app with really

00:17:58.066 --> 00:17:58.836 A:middle
detailed settings.

00:17:59.186 --> 00:18:00.246 A:middle
And they've done a great job

00:17:59.186 --> 00:18:00.246 A:middle
And they've done a great job

00:18:00.246 --> 00:18:00.936 A:middle
with their design.

00:18:01.166 --> 00:18:02.096 A:middle
There's like a great sense of

00:18:02.096 --> 00:18:03.396 A:middle
hierarchy and all of their

00:18:03.526 --> 00:18:05.486 A:middle
content is tailored to my

00:18:05.486 --> 00:18:05.936 A:middle
interests.

00:18:06.256 --> 00:18:07.726 A:middle
And when I drill down and see

00:18:07.726 --> 00:18:09.456 A:middle
the screen, they have specific

00:18:09.456 --> 00:18:10.926 A:middle
details for each type of

00:18:10.976 --> 00:18:11.916 A:middle
notification that you can

00:18:11.916 --> 00:18:12.346 A:middle
receive.

00:18:12.666 --> 00:18:13.686 A:middle
You know, basketball is

00:18:13.686 --> 00:18:14.586 A:middle
different than baseball.

00:18:14.586 --> 00:18:15.876 A:middle
Right. I have all the controls

00:18:15.876 --> 00:18:17.736 A:middle
that I need to receive exactly

00:18:17.736 --> 00:18:19.216 A:middle
the right notifications from

00:18:19.216 --> 00:18:19.736 A:middle
ESPN.

00:18:20.216 --> 00:18:22.916 A:middle
And "The New York Times" app is

00:18:22.916 --> 00:18:23.276 A:middle
great.

00:18:23.276 --> 00:18:24.876 A:middle
I have the options to configure

00:18:24.876 --> 00:18:26.106 A:middle
the different categories or

00:18:26.106 --> 00:18:27.066 A:middle
different sections that are

00:18:27.066 --> 00:18:27.606 A:middle
alerting me.

00:18:28.496 --> 00:18:30.626 A:middle
You know I might not find sports

00:18:30.626 --> 00:18:32.196 A:middle
or politics helpful, but I can

00:18:32.196 --> 00:18:33.736 A:middle
still receive breaking news and

00:18:33.736 --> 00:18:34.536 A:middle
top stories.

00:18:34.986 --> 00:18:35.976 A:middle
And I think this is really smart

00:18:35.976 --> 00:18:36.966 A:middle
for "The New York Times" to have

00:18:36.966 --> 00:18:37.396 A:middle
implemented.

00:18:37.756 --> 00:18:38.666 A:middle
Because not everyone may

00:18:38.666 --> 00:18:40.596 A:middle
appreciate interruptions every

00:18:40.596 --> 00:18:42.106 A:middle
single category that they offer.

00:18:42.886 --> 00:18:43.976 A:middle
So, for allowing this topic

00:18:43.976 --> 00:18:45.876 A:middle
level control, it assures people

00:18:46.276 --> 00:18:47.706 A:middle
to configure the experience to

00:18:47.706 --> 00:18:49.346 A:middle
their liking without resorting

00:18:49.346 --> 00:18:51.376 A:middle
to turning off all notifications

00:18:51.696 --> 00:18:52.336 A:middle
from that app.

00:18:53.796 --> 00:18:54.896 A:middle
So, it's really important, this

00:18:54.896 --> 00:18:56.136 A:middle
set of control is supported in

00:18:56.136 --> 00:18:57.746 A:middle
your app in a well-designed way.

00:18:57.746 --> 00:18:58.526 A:middle
All right.

00:18:59.736 --> 00:19:01.216 A:middle
So, those are the important

00:18:59.736 --> 00:19:01.216 A:middle
So, those are the important

00:19:01.216 --> 00:19:02.376 A:middle
things to remember when creating

00:19:02.376 --> 00:19:03.096 A:middle
notifications.

00:19:03.096 --> 00:19:04.166 A:middle
Now, you're going to be sending

00:19:04.166 --> 00:19:05.196 A:middle
out some really valuable

00:19:05.196 --> 00:19:05.876 A:middle
information.

00:19:07.176 --> 00:19:08.596 A:middle
The next thing is to talk about

00:19:08.596 --> 00:19:09.716 A:middle
notification grouping.

00:19:10.046 --> 00:19:11.426 A:middle
And this is a new feature in iOS

00:19:11.486 --> 00:19:12.926 A:middle
12 to help everyone keep their

00:19:12.926 --> 00:19:14.486 A:middle
notifications, you know all

00:19:14.486 --> 00:19:15.436 A:middle
those great, and valuable

00:19:15.436 --> 00:19:17.096 A:middle
content you'll be receiving,

00:19:17.846 --> 00:19:18.516 A:middle
more organized.

00:19:19.016 --> 00:19:21.176 A:middle
So, in iOS, we've always

00:19:21.176 --> 00:19:22.726 A:middle
appreciated the convenience of

00:19:22.726 --> 00:19:24.036 A:middle
seeing notifications on the lock

00:19:24.036 --> 00:19:24.356 A:middle
screen.

00:19:25.536 --> 00:19:26.826 A:middle
The chronological list is really

00:19:26.826 --> 00:19:27.766 A:middle
helpful to organize.

00:19:29.816 --> 00:19:30.936 A:middle
And it's great to see the

00:19:30.936 --> 00:19:32.616 A:middle
content of notifications without

00:19:32.616 --> 00:19:33.446 A:middle
having to interact with the

00:19:33.446 --> 00:19:34.096 A:middle
device.

00:19:34.916 --> 00:19:36.266 A:middle
You just pick up the phone and

00:19:36.266 --> 00:19:37.596 A:middle
everything is there, it's all

00:19:37.596 --> 00:19:37.966 A:middle
visible.

00:19:39.366 --> 00:19:40.656 A:middle
But you know, there gets to be a

00:19:40.656 --> 00:19:41.606 A:middle
point where that long

00:19:41.606 --> 00:19:43.326 A:middle
chronological list starts to

00:19:43.326 --> 00:19:43.956 A:middle
break down.

00:19:44.516 --> 00:19:45.296 A:middle
Whenever there's a lot of

00:19:45.296 --> 00:19:46.416 A:middle
different content coming on the

00:19:46.416 --> 00:19:47.106 A:middle
screen, right?

00:19:47.106 --> 00:19:48.496 A:middle
Especially multiple messages, or

00:19:48.496 --> 00:19:49.276 A:middle
if you have group chats

00:19:49.276 --> 00:19:50.526 A:middle
happening all at the same time,

00:19:50.696 --> 00:19:51.756 A:middle
it's really difficult to follow.

00:19:51.756 --> 00:19:53.216 A:middle
So, that's when we decided to

00:19:53.216 --> 00:19:54.586 A:middle
start grouping notifications.

00:19:55.696 --> 00:19:56.946 A:middle
Now, all your related content is

00:19:56.946 --> 00:19:57.796 A:middle
organized together.

00:19:58.466 --> 00:20:01.016 A:middle
A simple tap on each group

00:19:58.466 --> 00:20:01.016 A:middle
A simple tap on each group

00:20:01.016 --> 00:20:02.496 A:middle
expands it open and you can

00:20:02.496 --> 00:20:04.206 A:middle
interact with each notification

00:20:04.426 --> 00:20:04.956 A:middle
individually.

00:20:05.386 --> 00:20:07.196 A:middle
And by default, notifications

00:20:07.196 --> 00:20:08.646 A:middle
will group together by app.

00:20:09.246 --> 00:20:11.226 A:middle
And for most cases, that make

00:20:11.226 --> 00:20:11.796 A:middle
sense.

00:20:12.256 --> 00:20:13.716 A:middle
But you know there's some

00:20:13.716 --> 00:20:14.946 A:middle
circumstances when sorting them

00:20:14.946 --> 00:20:16.736 A:middle
out in a more detailed way can

00:20:16.736 --> 00:20:17.286 A:middle
be helpful.

00:20:17.376 --> 00:20:19.236 A:middle
And messages is a perfect

00:20:19.236 --> 00:20:19.686 A:middle
example.

00:20:19.856 --> 00:20:21.136 A:middle
I don't think it would be the

00:20:21.136 --> 00:20:22.646 A:middle
most useful thing to see every

00:20:22.646 --> 00:20:23.916 A:middle
missed message from every

00:20:23.916 --> 00:20:25.376 A:middle
conversation thread and group

00:20:25.376 --> 00:20:26.786 A:middle
chat you're having all lumped

00:20:26.786 --> 00:20:28.176 A:middle
together into a single group.

00:20:29.186 --> 00:20:30.356 A:middle
So, to more clearly organize

00:20:30.356 --> 00:20:32.136 A:middle
everything we create a new group

00:20:32.326 --> 00:20:33.486 A:middle
for each conversation.

00:20:33.816 --> 00:20:34.836 A:middle
And we call each individual

00:20:34.836 --> 00:20:35.866 A:middle
group a thread.

00:20:37.276 --> 00:20:38.696 A:middle
So, let's take a moment and talk

00:20:38.696 --> 00:20:40.556 A:middle
about notification threads and

00:20:40.556 --> 00:20:41.896 A:middle
what the best ways may be to

00:20:41.896 --> 00:20:42.886 A:middle
organize your content.

00:20:43.336 --> 00:20:44.686 A:middle
So, notification grouping uses

00:20:44.686 --> 00:20:46.276 A:middle
the existing thread identifier

00:20:46.276 --> 00:20:46.636 A:middle
API.

00:20:47.346 --> 00:20:49.016 A:middle
This API was introduced as part

00:20:49.016 --> 00:20:50.326 A:middle
of the notification content

00:20:50.326 --> 00:20:50.956 A:middle
extensions.

00:20:51.316 --> 00:20:53.366 A:middle
We expanded its use to create

00:20:53.366 --> 00:20:54.326 A:middle
notification groups.

00:20:55.056 --> 00:20:56.736 A:middle
The thread identifier can be any

00:20:56.736 --> 00:20:58.256 A:middle
string that you want and the

00:20:58.256 --> 00:20:59.626 A:middle
notifications with the same

00:20:59.626 --> 00:21:01.216 A:middle
thread identifier are all

00:20:59.626 --> 00:21:01.216 A:middle
thread identifier are all

00:21:01.216 --> 00:21:01.826 A:middle
grouped together.

00:21:02.296 --> 00:21:02.756 A:middle
That's it.

00:21:03.016 --> 00:21:03.646 A:middle
Super simple.

00:21:06.456 --> 00:21:07.556 A:middle
So, threads make a lot of sense

00:21:07.556 --> 00:21:08.256 A:middle
and you have separate

00:21:08.256 --> 00:21:09.756 A:middle
conversations to group together.

